description: SIMULATION THEORY FILMExperience on IMAX on 17 August: https://www.imax.com/museDigital download available 21 August: http://muse.mu/filmDeluxe box sets out 11 December. Pre-order now!From February to October of 2019 MUSE took their Simulation Theory Tour to over 28 countries and played in front of more than 1 MILLION people.¬† Now fans will be able to experience the spectacle and more,¬† beginning August 17th when ‚ÄúMUSE - Simulation Theory: The IMAX Experience‚Äù will be available exclusively in select IMAX Theaters around the world and¬† August 21st when the Simulation Theory movie will be available for rent or download on iTunes, Amazon and Google Play (distribution will be via Eagle Rock Entertainment). For more information please go to http://muse.mu/filmConceived and filmed at London‚Äôs O2 Arena in September 2019 the film directed by Lance Drake, (who also directed all the promo videos for Simulation Theory album) and Produced by Muse, Pulse Films, Lance Drake, Jesse-Lee Stout and Matthew Bellamy, follows a team of scientists as they investigate the source of a paranormal anomaly appearing around the world. Blurring the lines between narrative and concert film, virtual and reality, Muse‚Äôs most theatrical tour to date launches the viewer through a supernatural spectacle, questioning the world around us.Says Drake, ‚Äúthe goal for Simulation Theory was to capture the scale of the electrifying live show and to expand upon its connection to the DNA of the world we built for the past three years in music videos for Muse. In a strange turn, the film‚Äôs alternate reality eerily started to mirror our own.‚ÄùFans can pre order tickets for the IMAX showings http://imax.com/museThe film has also undergone IMAX‚Äôs cutting-edge proprietary Digital Media Re-Mastering (DMR) and sound mixing process to take advantage of the stunning visuals and precision audio of the IMAX¬Æ Experience. In IMAX, MUSE fans will be immersed in a cinematic world¬† of unmatched scope and clarity, surrounded by next-generation precision audio that delivers pitch-perfect tuning and pin-point accuracy in custom-designed IMAX theatres.Theater safety measures will comply with governmental and exhibitor guidelines. Examples of typical measures taken may include but are not limited to use of masks by employees, social distancing and capacity constraints, as well as increased sanitation efforts. Please contact your local exhibitor for more information on their specific precautions.Available for pre order on the same day will be 2 different limited edition deluxe box sets which will be available via muse.mu and physical retail. To celebrate the release of the Deluxe box sets, MUSE also teamed up with Marvel Comics to create and release a custom Simulation Theory comic book and limited-edition poster.

description: SIMULATION THEORY FILMExperience on IMAX on 17 August: https://www.imax.com/museDigital download available 21 August: http://muse.mu/filmDeluxe box sets out 11 December. Pre-order now!From February to October of 2019 MUSE took their Simulation Theory Tour to over 28 countries and played in front of more than 1 MILLION people.¬† Now fans will be able to experience the spectacle and more,¬† beginning August 17th when ‚ÄúMUSE - Simulation Theory: The IMAX Experience‚Äù will be available exclusively in select IMAX Theaters around the world and¬† August 21st when the Simulation Theory movie will be available for rent or download on iTunes, Amazon and Google Play (distribution will be via Eagle Rock Entertainment). For more information please go to http://muse.mu/filmConceived and filmed at London‚Äôs O2 Arena in September 2019 the film directed by Lance Drake, (who also directed all the promo videos for Simulation Theory album) and Produced by Muse, Pulse Films, Lance Drake, Jesse-Lee Stout and Matthew Bellamy, follows a team of scientists as they investigate the source of a paranormal anomaly appearing around the world. Blurring the lines between narrative and concert film, virtual and reality, Muse‚Äôs most theatrical tour to date launches the viewer through a supernatural spectacle, questioning the world around us.Says Drake, ‚Äúthe goal for Simulation Theory was to capture the scale of the electrifying live show and to expand upon its connection to the DNA of the world we built for the past three years in music videos for Muse. In a strange turn, the film‚Äôs alternate reality eerily started to mirror our own.‚ÄùFans can pre order tickets for the IMAX showings http://imax.com/museThe film has also undergone IMAX‚Äôs cutting-edge proprietary Digital Media Re-Mastering (DMR) and sound mixing process to take advantage of the stunning visuals and precision audio of the IMAX¬Æ Experience. In IMAX, MUSE fans will be immersed in a cinematic world¬† of unmatched scope and clarity, surrounded by next-generation precision audio that delivers pitch-perfect tuning and pin-point accuracy in custom-designed IMAX theatres.Theater safety measures will comply with governmental and exhibitor guidelines. Examples of typical measures taken may include but are not limited to use of masks by employees, social distancing and capacity constraints, as well as increased sanitation efforts. Please contact your local exhibitor for more information on their specific precautions.Available for pre order on the same day will be 2 different limited edition deluxe box sets which will be available via muse.mu and physical retail. To celebrate the release of the Deluxe box sets, MUSE also teamed up with Marvel Comics to create and release a custom Simulation Theory comic book and limited-edition poster.

description: En la Perla de Occidente, Guadalajara recibi√≥ a Puebla en partido correspondiente a la Jornada 3 del Guard1anes 2020 de la Liga BBVA MX. Primero por el sector izquierdo mandando un tiro cruzado que no termin√≥ por cerrar y se escurri√≥ a un costado del poste derecho de la Franja; en tanto, al minuto 41, por la derecha, se desprendi√≥ de la marca y de pierna izquierda, con parte interna busc√≥ el √°ngulo superior m√°s alejado, pero el esf√©rico se neg√≥ a caer a tiempo. En la segunda mitad los visitantes iniciaron con mayor posesi√≥n y adelantaron l√≠neas, pero Chivas avis√≥ peligro primero con un servicio cruzado que en los linderos del √°rea estuvo a punto de rematar Uriel Antuna. Juan Reynoso mand√≥ a la cancha a Brayan Angulo y el lateral se hizo presente a la ofensiva con pocos minutos en el campo al mandar un servicio al √°rea, el cual en dos tiempos, Santiago Orme√±o, control√≥ con mucha clase, para de media vuelta y con la marca pegada, disparar con potencia a primer poste. Pese a tener un hombre menos en la cancha, Chivas sigui√≥ buscando la porter√≠a Poblana y Jes√∫s S√°nchez tuvo una buena oportunidad, pero precipit√≥ un testarazo que se fue muy desviado. description: SIMULATION THEORY FILMExperience on IMAX on 17 August: https://www.imax.com/museDigital download available 21 August: http://muse.mu/filmDeluxe box sets out 11 December. Pre-order now!From February to October of 2019 MUSE took their Simulation Theory Tour to over 28 countries and played in front of more than 1 MILLION people.¬† Now fans will be able to experience the spectacle and more,¬† beginning August 17th when ‚ÄúMUSE - Simulation Theory: The IMAX Experience‚Äù will be available exclusively in select IMAX Theaters around the world and¬† August 21st when the Simulation Theory movie will be available for rent or download on iTunes, Amazon and Google Play (distribution will be via Eagle Rock Entertainment). For more information please go to http://muse.mu/filmConceived and filmed at London‚Äôs O2 Arena in September 2019 the film directed by Lance Drake, (who also directed all the promo videos for Simulation Theory album) and Produced by Muse, Pulse Films, Lance Drake, Jesse-Lee Stout and Matthew Bellamy, follows a team of scientists as they investigate the source of a paranormal anomaly appearing around the world. Blurring the lines between narrative and concert film, virtual and reality, Muse‚Äôs most theatrical tour to date launches the viewer through a supernatural spectacle, questioning the world around us.Says Drake, ‚Äúthe goal for Simulation Theory was to capture the scale of the electrifying live show and to expand upon its connection to the DNA of the world we built for the past three years in music videos for Muse. In a strange turn, the film‚Äôs alternate reality eerily started to mirror our own.‚ÄùFans can pre order tickets for the IMAX showings http://imax.com/museThe film has also undergone IMAX‚Äôs cutting-edge proprietary Digital Media Re-Mastering (DMR) and sound mixing process to take advantage of the stunning visuals and precision audio of the IMAX¬Æ Experience. In IMAX, MUSE fans will be immersed in a cinematic world¬† of unmatched scope and clarity, surrounded by next-generation precision audio that delivers pitch-perfect tuning and pin-point accuracy in custom-designed IMAX theatres.Theater safety measures will comply with governmental and exhibitor guidelines. Examples of typical measures taken may include but are not limited to use of masks by employees, social distancing and capacity constraints, as well as increased sanitation efforts. Please contact your local exhibitor for more information on their specific precautions.Available for pre order on the same day will be 2 different limited edition deluxe box sets which will be available via muse.mu and physical retail. To celebrate the release of the Deluxe box sets, MUSE also teamed up with Marvel Comics to create and release a custom Simulation Theory comic book and limited-edition poster.

description: SIMULATION THEORY FILMExperience on IMAX on 17 August: https://www.imax.com/museDigital download available 21 August: http://muse.mu/filmDeluxe box sets out 11 December. Pre-order now!From February to October of 2019 MUSE took their Simulation Theory Tour to over 28 countries and played in front of more than 1 MILLION people.¬† Now fans will be able to experience the spectacle and more,¬† beginning August 17th when ‚ÄúMUSE - Simulation Theory: The IMAX Experience‚Äù will be available exclusively in select IMAX Theaters around the world and¬† August 21st when the Simulation Theory movie will be available for rent or download on iTunes, Amazon and Google Play (distribution will be via Eagle Rock Entertainment). For more information please go to http://muse.mu/filmConceived and filmed at London‚Äôs O2 Arena in September 2019 the film directed by Lance Drake, (who also directed all the promo videos for Simulation Theory album) and Produced by Muse, Pulse Films, Lance Drake, Jesse-Lee Stout and Matthew Bellamy, follows a team of scientists as they investigate the source of a paranormal anomaly appearing around the world. Blurring the lines between narrative and concert film, virtual and reality, Muse‚Äôs most theatrical tour to date launches the viewer through a supernatural spectacle, questioning the world around us.Says Drake, ‚Äúthe goal for Simulation Theory was to capture the scale of the electrifying live show and to expand upon its connection to the DNA of the world we built for the past three years in music videos for Muse. In a strange turn, the film‚Äôs alternate reality eerily started to mirror our own.‚ÄùFans can pre order tickets for the IMAX showings http://imax.com/museThe film has also undergone IMAX‚Äôs cutting-edge proprietary Digital Media Re-Mastering (DMR) and sound mixing process to take advantage of the stunning visuals and precision audio of the IMAX¬Æ Experience. In IMAX, MUSE fans will be immersed in a cinematic world¬† of unmatched scope and clarity, surrounded by next-generation precision audio that delivers pitch-perfect tuning and pin-point accuracy in custom-designed IMAX theatres.Theater safety measures will comply with governmental and exhibitor guidelines. Examples of typical measures taken may include but are not limited to use of masks by employees, social distancing and capacity constraints, as well as increased sanitation efforts. Please contact your local exhibitor for more information on their specific precautions.Available for pre order on the same day will be 2 different limited edition deluxe box sets which will be available via muse.mu and physical retail. To celebrate the release of the Deluxe box sets, MUSE also teamed up with Marvel Comics to create and release a custom Simulation Theory comic book and limited-edition poster.
